This paper deals with the challenges of geocoding imprecise spatial expressions in English text, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), and Deep Learning (cs.DL).
